{"tid":1031662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國JY-27自稱世界最強反隱身雷達在敘利亞被以色列摧毀","createTime":"2019-02-21T20:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T01:57:20.000Z","uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06d36c3e823542ec9cd6344787f1fc56e467466f","tid":1031662,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1366038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1366038&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=008a8324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1366038</a><br />\n<br />\n中國製的JY27雷達在以色列空襲敘利亞的行動中被摧毀。（圖／翻攝自ImageSat Intl.）<br />\n記者林彥臣／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n以色列日前完成了打擊敘利亞首都大馬士革軍事目標的行動，只出動F-16就摧毀了俄羅斯製的Pantsir-S1（鎧甲-S1），另外中國製的JY27米波雷達也在空襲行動中遭到摧毀。對此王浩宇在臉書發文指出，「中國軍武，實戰就像垃圾。」<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇指出，以色列日前針對敘利亞首都大馬士革軍事目標進行摧毀行動，僅派出F-16戰機就順利炸毀了最先進的中國隱身雷達及俄國防空系統，其中，中國最先進的JY-27雷達，號稱對空最大探測距離達300公里，能探測到以色列空軍的F-35隱形戰鬥機，但實戰時卻連F-16都偵測不到，慘遭以色列空軍F-16戰機摧毀，證明中國軍武根本毫無實用性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtE1JB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtE1JB6.jpg&h=db2b0961&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae80b8d593008aa6aa00fcd56ab3f811eb1b9b5","tid":1031662,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e21a65791fe44686c40559b4b7cf2db32acf98e","tid":1031662,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4767ef34abf837984b918f56e1d0445ced2acff8","tid":1031662,"uid":85057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T21:09:34.000Z","msg":"贏了"},{"pid":"0f022af7eb1a6fd612287ff973429c5efd3cb7ae","tid":1031662,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T21:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca11f9b82d4a4b129f8535757a695a7d08966b89","tid":1031662,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T22:13:31.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"2e8bac449829e4dcee6a7b4dbe3ba759aab77ae6","tid":1031662,"uid":65473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"好耐啦bo ching"},{"pid":"f76a59675122df8b020276aa14fc829c0569e13c","tid":1031662,"uid":107574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06d36c3e823542ec9cd6344787f1fc56e467466f","tid":1031662,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T20:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1366038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1366038&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=008a8324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1366038</a><br />\n<br />\n中國製的JY27雷達在以色列空襲敘利亞的行動中被摧毀。（圖／翻攝自ImageSat Intl.）<br />\n記者林彥臣／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n以色列日前完成了打擊敘利亞首都大馬士革軍事目標的行動，只出動F-16就摧毀了俄羅斯製的Pantsir-S1（鎧甲-S1），另外中國製的JY27米波雷達也在空襲行動中遭到摧毀。對此王浩宇在臉書發文指出，「中國軍武，實戰就像垃圾。」<br />\n<br />\n王浩宇指出，以色列日前針對敘利亞首都大馬士革軍事目標進行摧毀行動，僅派出F-16戰機就順利炸毀了最先進的中國隱身雷達及俄國防空系統，其中，中國最先進的JY-27雷達，號稱對空最大探測距離達300公里，能探測到以色列空軍的F-35隱形戰鬥機，但實戰時卻連F-16都偵測不到，慘遭以色列空軍F-16戰機摧毀，證明中國軍武根本毫無實用性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtE1JB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtE1